    {
      "id": "PopularPost252949",
      "post_content": "@izzet  \n  \nIt is slightly different, hence (part of) the reason they didn't change it.   \n  \nIn this case, the player may choose an untapped creature, and tap it before the Declare Blockers step to not have to block. Likewise they could choose something like Tormented soul. If it was \"Crashing Boars must be blocked by at least one creature if able\" The player would have to choose some creature they control that is able to block it. Honestly your version would be better (opponents having the option is always a powerbreaker, even if it is this circumstantial.) ",
      "posted_by": "orisiti",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost252949\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_post\">@izzet<br/><br/>It is slightly different, hence (part of) the reason they didn't change it.  <br/><br/>In this case, the player may choose an untapped creature, and tap it before the Declare Blockers step to not have to block.  Likewise they could choose something like Tormented soul.  If it was \"Crashing Boars must be blocked by at least one creature if able\"  The player would have to choose some creature they control that is able to block it.  Honestly your version would be better (opponents having the option is always a powerbreaker, even if it is this circumstantial.) </span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '252949'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy22750\">orisiti</span>\r\n                                (6/26/2012 4:59:59 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../